            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in v2.3-beta.5.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Native search field on the Home Dashboard — find projects by name, transcript, or caption text</li>
                    <li>Redesigned toolbar with contextual Find and Export buttons</li>
                    <li>New Export menu with format options: Final Cut Pro, Final Cut Pro Subtitle, DaVinci Resolve, Adobe Premiere Pro, and SRT</li>
                    <li>Removed redundant burger menu and duplicate export button</li>
                    <li>Version label now reads from bundle info and stays in sync</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
        </item>
        
